    "Further, it requires students to conduct time-intensive review of the precision, credibility, and authenticity of AIfacilitated content.",
    "In addition, given that academic writing demands a meticulous interplay of discipline-specific knowledge and unwavering adherence to scholarly standards (e.g., rigorous and credible sources and evidence), AI hallucinations undermine the very purpose of academic writing and scholarly contributions.",
    "Second, AI's lack of contextual understanding was another significant challenge to effective GenAI-assisted writing.",
    "For academic writing tasks, students need to go beyond summarizing the relevant information.",
    "They are required to situate ideas, arguments, or practices in a larger context to construct the readers' view of a broadscale situation, and call attention to the relationships that surround an issue (Epting, 2018)."
